Retention Strategies: To reduce attrition, companies should focus on increasing employee satisfaction by targeting key areas like job role alignment, salary adjustments, and employee engagement programs.

Performance Improvement: Predictive models can help HR teams focus on employees who may need additional support or training, leading to better overall performance and productivity.

Future Scope: Further analysis could include more advanced machine learning techniques or additional features such as employee satisfaction surveys or exit interview data for more accurate predictions.
